data.description:
Welcome to a cozy 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in Rasco Farms subdivision.. The  eat in kitchen has plenty of cupboard space and  overlooks the living area. Main bathroom has a  tub/shower combo. The primary bathroom  has a large walk in shower.  Backyard has a deck that is perfect for family gatherings and being outside on a fall day.
Start the new year in this home.
